- fix `AdjustmentMethod=1` the default ini issue that cannot use F9/F10 slower/faster function when using giuroll

- btw F6 info function may make your game drop FPS so not recommend. Now we have another info mod based on shady-loader's lua script, which is easier to edit and more powerful. [Check out here in #Hisouten.](https://discord.com/channels/167593473854144512/1354448046569689231/1355084943461715990)
